Snail Bob 8: Island Story is a single player puzzle game with lots of interesting aspects offering easy gaming to players. It is an exciting game with lots of new changes made to gaming compared to its predecessors. The game is all about guiding the little snail Bob navigate through its way and get to the exit.The obstacles on the way can be hurting or can kill Bob and hence the player has to take Bob to the exit safely.
